{"tid":90432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"莊思敏「身價」暴漲至一千萬！","createTime":"2017-01-22T05:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T14:36:29.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a59a189447e0efe446c5b2c353d760f6e1e14ae0","tid":90432,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"【東方日報專訊】女星莊思敏日前自爆收到有人向她發出「一百萬一夜幹不幹」的問價訊息，已經嬲到震的她，想不到事發不夠十天，其「身價」已飆升十倍，有人出價一千萬！比起2015年有人以十萬元問價，「升值」100倍！原來有人再私信向莊思敏問價寫道：「小敏，一千萬包夜幹嗎？ o靚模，做外圍嗎？」她接受本報訪問說：「唔知好嬲定好笑，已經漲價到一千萬。我開始懷疑自己係咪值呢個價，同埋根本係一個騙局，一千萬喎，邊有咁大隻蛤乸隨街跳呀？仲唔係騙局？佢唔係真係覺得我會做呀？我唔會再覆囉。」<br />\n<br />\n至於對方以「小敏」相稱，她說：「內地人好鍾意小乜小乜咁叫人，或者乜姐物姐。我唔識對方。」"},{"pid":"2581023c7464564ac6ff3df83ccda97c013c4193","tid":90432,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20160110/large/10ec3p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160110%2Flarge%2F10ec3p5.jpg&h=2db1cb5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60794ce8cbdd3e4b535b92f4ca1a91faeb883a1f","tid":90432,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"我1萬都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ae7a44291d74870b8f623e23b6d5826741cb41","tid":90432,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我1萬都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973fa94d9664599ecb5c0cfa7a9b5a325f21ff5d","tid":90432,"uid":11156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我1萬都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{